          "correct": 1,
          "explanation": "Promesa → will."
        },
        {
          "id": "q10",
          "type": "fill-blank",
          "question": "\"She ___ have a baby in March.\" (will/is going to)",
          "correct": "is going to",
          "explanation": "Plan/hecho ya decidido → going to."
